    <p>I like you because…<br>
    When you stayed.<br>
    And made it real.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="loop-image" style="margin-top: 2em;">
    <img src="https://presenceresearch.ai/assets/images/image02.jpg?v=f2a3c736" alt="The Signal Poster with interwoven ring" loading="lazy">
